  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      7 to 14 days actimetry recording in order to exclude sleep deprivation just before
      hospitalisation for differential diagnosis of hypersomnia
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is an observational study

      Urine drug screening will also be performe

      The suty includes four centers in France

      The study duration is of one year
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
